{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo winnu Akmina-Kalns\nne irr itt ka muhſu Akmina-\nKalns/ pahr to irr muhſu Eenaid-\nneeki paſchi Teefatajt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo winnu Wihna-Rohks\nirr no Sodemas Wihna-Rohka/\nun no Gomorras Tihrumteem/\nwinnu Wihna-Rekkari irr Schul-\ntu Rekkari / teem irr ruhktas\nOhgas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnu Wihns irr Puh-\nfu-Dſellons / un breeſiniga Oh-\ndſchu Schults.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wuj ne irr tas pee man-\nnim paſlehpts / aissehgelehts\nmannas Mantag?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Man peederr ta Atreeb-\nſhana un ta Atmakſafchana/\nſatwa Laika ſlihdehs winnu Kah-\nja / jo winnu Nomaitaschannas\nDeena irr tuwu/ un tas/ kas\nwinneem nahkams irr steidſahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS teefahs\nfawus Landis/ un pahr fatweem\nKalpeem nahkſees winnam ſchebl.\nJo wiꞥſch eerandſihs / ka tas\nSpehts aifgahjis irr/ ka ne nee-\nfa irr/ kas aiſſlehpts un kas at-\nſtahte irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad faſzihs wiꞥſch: kur\nirr winnu Deewi/ tas Akmina-\nKalns/ us ko tee zerreja ?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kuren Upputa Taakus\no, tee ehde/ kuren Dſerrama-Up-\npuka Wihnu tee dſehre / laid tee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangajt nu/ka Es eſmu\nka es pats eſmu / un ne ween\nDeews lihds ar mannim/ es ne\nkauju un darri dſihwu / es e\nwainoju un Dſeedinaju / un ne\nweens irr/ kas no mannas Roh-\nkus warr iſglahbt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es pazelfschu mann\nRohku prett Debbeſi/ un faſzi-\nſchu: Es dſihwoju muhſchigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad es manna Sohbix\nSibbinu trihſchu / un mann\nRohka pee Sohdibas isſteepfees\ntad liſchu es to Atreebfchan-\nus manneem Prettineefeem a-\ngreestees / un atmakkaschu man-\nneem Eenaidneefeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es peedfirđinaſchu man-\nnas Bultas ar Affini/ un man-\nSohbins ehdihſ Meefas ar t\nNokautu un Guhstitu Affint/ a-\nAtreebfchanahin pahr ta Eenaid-\nneeka Galwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Gawilejeet juhs Pagam-\nar winna Landim/ jo wiꞥſch at-\nreebs fawu Kalpu Affini / u-\nlks to Atreebfchannu us fatwee-\nPrettineefeem atreebtees/ un ap-\nschehlofees pahr fawu Seimmi-\nun pahr fatweem Landim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus nahze un rum-\nnaja wiﬀus ſchihs Dſeefina-\nWahrdus preekſch to Lauſchu-\nAufim/ wiꞥſch un Josuiis/ Nun-\nna Dehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad wiꞥſch nu pabeidſi-\nbij wiﬀus ſchohs Wahrdus u-\nwiﬀu Ifraelu runnaht/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
